Complete Web Development Bootcamp - Reading Materials

Master full-stack web development with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, and Node.js.

Course Syllabus:
1. HTML Fundamentals
2. CSS Layouts and Flexbox
3. Responsive Design with CSS Grid
4. JavaScript Essentials
5. DOM Manipulation
6. Async JavaScript and APIs
7. React Fundamentals
8. React Hooks and State Management
9. Node.js and Express
10. Database Integration
11. Deployment and Production

Key Topics Covered:
- Frontend Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)
- Modern JavaScript (ES6+)
- React Framework
- Backend Development (Node.js, Express)
- Database Design (MongoDB/SQL)
- API Development
- Authentication and Security
- Deployment Strategies

Tools and Technologies:
- VS Code
- Git and GitHub
- Chrome DevTools
- Postman for API testing
- MongoDB Atlas
- Heroku/Netlify for deployment

This comprehensive bootcamp will take you from zero to job-ready developer!